{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0199UGc41MdKdNgeX8Ha9uzC","type":"tool_result","content":"  1050тЖТ\n  1051тЖТ### Survey findings (for future sessions)\n  1052тЖТ- **trustedCircle**: Now has linting. All Tier 1-3 features complete, 136 tests, CI with lint/check/test/build/smoke.\n  1053тЖТ- **groceryGenius**: Missing standalone ESLint setup (currently uses `next lint` which may break on Next.js upgrades like runeval did)\n  1054тЖТ- **All repos**: Clean audit (except known unfixable transitive deps), tests passing, CI active, branches clean\n  1055тЖТ\n  1056тЖТ---\n  1057тЖТ\n  1058тЖТ## 2026-03-20 тАФ Run 44\n  1059тЖТ\n  1060тЖТ### What was done\n  1061тЖТ\n  1062тЖТ**trustedCircle тАФ Comprehensive WCAG accessibility pass (PRs #44-#45, auto-merged)**\n  1063тЖТ- **Card component**: Added keyboard support (Enter/Space to activate) with focus ring for all clickable cards across the app\n  1064тЖТ- **ReactionButtons**: Added `aria-pressed` toggle state and `aria-label` with counts on both helpful/agree buttons\n  1065тЖТ- **SortPills**: Added `aria-pressed` on active pill, `role=\"group\"` with label on container\n  1066тЖТ- **StarRating**: Added `role=\"img\"` with descriptive `aria-label` (\"Rating: X.X out of 5 stars\")\n  1067тЖТ- **TrustBadges**: Added `aria-label` on badges, `aria-hidden` on decorative icons\n  1068тЖТ- **Header**: `aria-label` on nav, search form `role=\"search\"`, `sr-only` label for search input, `aria-current=\"page\"` on active nav link, `aria-label` on all nav links (for mobile icon-only view)\n  1069тЖТ- **App.tsx**: Wrapped page content in `<main>` landmark\n  1070тЖТ- **ReviewerSelector (ComparePage)**: Added `aria-haspopup=\"listbox\"`, `aria-expanded`, `role=\"listbox\"`/`role=\"option\"`, Escape key to close\n  1071тЖТ- **All back buttons** (4 pages): Added `aria-label`\n  1072тЖТ- **All search inputs** (3 locations): Associated `<label>` elements via `htmlFor`/`id`\n  1073тЖТ- **All filter pill groups** (3 pages): `role=\"group\"` with `aria-label`, `aria-pressed` on each pill\n  1074тЖТ- **40+ decorative Lucide icons**: Marked `aria-hidden=\"true\"` across 14 files\n  1075тЖТ- **Non-semantic interactive elements**: Replaced clickable `<span>`s with `<button>`s in ReviewCard and CirclePage FeedCard; wrapped clickable `<h2>` content in `<button>` on ComparePage\n  1076тЖТ- **Pagination (CategoryPage)**: Wrapped in `<nav aria-label=\"Pagination\">`, added `aria-label` on prev/next buttons\n  1077тЖТ- **Follow button (PersonPage)**: Added `aria-pressed` toggle state\n  1078тЖТ- **Load more button (CirclePage)**: Added `aria-busy` during loading\n  1079тЖТ- Result: 0 lint errors, 0 type errors, 136 tests passing, build clean\n  1080тЖТ\n  1081тЖТ### Survey findings (for future sessions)\n  1082тЖТ- **trustedCircle**: Now fully accessible. All Tier 1-3 features complete, 136 tests, CI with lint/check/test/build/smoke.\n  1083тЖТ- **groceryGenius**: Already has standalone ESLint (Vite project, not Next.js тАФ previous note was incorrect). Already had WCAG pass (Run 40).\n  1084тЖТ- **promptlibrary**: Already had WCAG pass (Run 41) and ESLint (Run 42).\n  1085тЖТ- **Remaining a11y opportunities**: runeval (main product, no a11y pass yet), valueSortify, pezantTools\n  1086тЖТ- **All repos**: Clean audit (except known unfixable transitive deps), tests passing, CI active, branches clean\n  1087тЖТ"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6299f222-4d85-46bc-988f-b18dcc539a25","uuid":"b086d591-284d-4d49-acea-b0bf3897eff2","timestamp":"2026-03-20T13:11:23.388Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"REDACTED_REPOS_ROOT/autonomousDev/logs/progress.md","content":"\n### Survey findings (for future sessions)\n- **trustedCircle**: Now has linting. All Tier 1-3 features complete, 136 tests, CI with lint/check/test/build/smoke.\n- **groceryGenius**: Missing standalone ESLint setup (currently uses `next lint` which may break on Next.js upgrades like runeval did)\n- **All repos**: Clean audit (except known unfixable transitive deps), tests passing, CI active, branches clean\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-20 тАФ Run 44\n\n### What was done\n\n**trustedCircle тАФ Comprehensive WCAG accessibility pass (PRs #44-#45, auto-merged)**\n- **Card component**: Added keyboard support (Enter/Space to activate) with focus ring for all clickable cards across the app\n- **ReactionButtons**: Added `aria-pressed` toggle state and `aria-label` with counts on both helpful/agree buttons\n- **SortPills**: Added `aria-pressed` on active pill, `role=\"group\"` with label on container\n- **StarRating**: Added `role=\"img\"` with descriptive `aria-label` (\"Rating: X.X out of 5 stars\")\n- **TrustBadges**: Added `aria-label` on badges, `aria-hidden` on decorative icons\n- **Header**: `aria-label` on nav, search form `role=\"search\"`, `sr-only` label for search input, `aria-current=\"page\"` on active nav link, `aria-label` on all nav links (for mobile icon-only view)\n- **App.tsx**: Wrapped page content in `<main>` landmark\n- **ReviewerSelector (ComparePage)**: Added `aria-haspopup=\"listbox\"`, `aria-expanded`, `role=\"listbox\"`/`role=\"option\"`, Escape key to close\n- **All back buttons** (4 pages): Added `aria-label`\n- **All search inputs** (3 locations): Associated `<label>` elements via `htmlFor`/`id`\n- **All filter pill groups** (3 pages): `role=\"group\"` with `aria-label`, `aria-pressed` on each pill\n- **40+ decorative Lucide icons**: Marked `aria-hidden=\"true\"` across 14 files\n- **Non-semantic interactive elements**: Replaced clickable `<span>`s with `<button>`s in ReviewCard and CirclePage FeedCard; wrapped clickable `<h2>` content in `<button>` on ComparePage\n- **Pagination (CategoryPage)**: Wrapped in `<nav aria-label=\"Pagination\">`, added `aria-label` on prev/next buttons\n- **Follow button (PersonPage)**: Added `aria-pressed` toggle state\n- **Load more button (CirclePage)**: Added `aria-busy` during loading\n- Result: 0 lint errors, 0 type errors, 136 tests passing, build clean\n\n### Survey findings (for future sessions)\n- **trustedCircle**: Now fully accessible. All Tier 1-3 features complete, 136 tests, CI with lint/check/test/build/smoke.\n- **groceryGenius**: Already has standalone ESLint (Vite project, not Next.js тАФ previous note was incorrect). Already had WCAG pass (Run 40).\n- **promptlibrary**: Already had WCAG pass (Run 41) and ESLint (Run 42).\n- **Remaining a11y opportunities**: runeval (main product, no a11y pass yet), valueSortify, pezantTools\n- **All repos**: Clean audit (except known unfixable transitive deps), tests passing, CI active, branches clean\n","numLines":38,"startLine":1050,"totalLines":1087}}}
